HasAttachHandlers, HasHandlers, EventListener, HasVisibility, IsRenderable, IsWidget, InputFeedbackListener, ReferenceCodeListener, WidgetInputListener
public class PdListBox
extends PdWidget

A list of choices to the user. When an option is selected, it triggers an ActionEvent. By default, a PdListBox has graphical vertical orientation displaying the name of the option and the reference code for the option in a single line.

CSS Style Rules

.pwListbox
the outer element.
.pwListboxTitle
the title of the listbox
.pwListboxItem
An item of the listbox
.pwListboxItemLabel
The label of the item of the listbox
.pwListboxItemReferencecode
The reference of the item of the listbox

Author:
Jorge C. S. Cardoso
